@EU_Commission @FES_EU Yes, there are problems but no-one, except an outright liar, can deny that the benefits hugely outweigh the downsides. 
These problems could be addressed, are being addressed (belatedly) and by the elected representatives of every member country.
All votes are from all members.

@EU_Commission  Please consider the cons of #article13 and how it will hinder and censor creators and artists.

People agree more should be done to help copyright issues, But filtering everything and suppressing people's freedom doesn't feel right.

Thank you.

